    <item>
      <title>司法部改组后特朗普亲信挑选的 FBI 官员遭批评</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-s-loyalist-pick-for-fbi-faces-critics-after-doj-shake-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统通过一系列备忘录和指令迅速采取行动重塑美国执法部门，要求司法部员工关注移民执法等首要任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-s-loyalist-pick-for-fbi-faces-critics-after-doj-shake-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 20:54:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前参议员梅内德斯因金条贿赂案被判 11 年有期徒刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/ex-senator-bob-menendez-gets-11-years-for-gold-bar-bribe-scheme</link>
      <description><![CDATA[鲍勃·梅嫩德斯因充当埃及的外国代理人并收受金条和其他贿赂而被判处 11 年监禁，检察官称这可能是有史以来美国参议员最严重的腐败案件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/ex-senator-bob-menendez-gets-11-years-for-gold-bar-bribe-scheme</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 20:44:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
